short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Find the GitHub repository for a site hosted on GitHub pages

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension provides a shortcut to the repository for sites hosted on GitHub pages. It works with sites on github.io, but it also detects sites that have a custom domain.

Click on the extension icon to check if a website is hosted on GitHub Pages.
